Constant Field Values

fbias

protected final double fbias

dimension

protected int dimension
This functions' dimension.

NOISE

protected double NOISE
Some functions introduce some noise. Having NOISE = 0.0 disables the introduction of this noise (for example for testing the fuctions). NOISE = 1 enables the introduction of noise.

BIAS_FITNESS

protected double BIAS_FITNESS
A bias is added to every function. If BIAS_FITNESS = 0.0, no bias is added.

epsilon

public static final double epsilon
Absolute error.
